<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Noted</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../style.css">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
</head>

<body style="background-color: black;">

    <div class="upper">
        <button id="signup">Sign up</button>
        <button id="signin">Sign in</button>
    </div>

    <div class="brand">
        <p class="eye">Noted</p>
    </div>
    <div class="main_landing">
        <div style="display: grid;margin-right: 2%;">
            <div class="eye_catcher">If it is not written down, it does not exist.</div>
            <div class="description">
                Noted is a sleek, intuitive note-taking app designed to capture your thoughts, ideas, and to-dos effortlessly. Whether you're jotting down quick notes, organizing detailed research, or creating to-do lists, Noted keeps everything neatly in one place.
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="image_landing">
            <img src="logo.PNG" class="logo">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="display">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="head">Simplicity</div>
            <div class="content">
            Noted, with its intuitive and user-friendly interface, empowers users to seamlessly carry out their daily essential tasks. From organizing schedules and managing to-do lists to capturing fleeting ideas and detailed notes, Noted ensures that everything you need is just a click away, helping you stay productive and focused throughout your day.
            <br />
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="head">Modern</div>
            <div class="content">
            Noted is designed to be a modern note-taking app that is both visually appealing and highly functional. It incorporates the latest design trends and technologies to provide users with a seamless and enjoyable experience. Noted incorporates AI to help you stay organized.
            <br/>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="head">Functional</div>
            <div class="content">
            Easily manipulate your notes, create new ones, and delete old ones. Noted is designed to be a functional and efficient note-taking app that helps you stay organized and focused. 
            <br />
            </div>
        </div>
  
    </div>

    
    <footer class="footer">
        <p>Noted 2025. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <p>
            <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a> |
            <a href="#">Terms of Service</a> |
            <a href="#">Contact Us</a>
        </p>
    </footer>
    <script src="../landing.js"></script>
</body>
</html>